## ðŸŽ¯ IMPLEMENTATION ORDER

1. **App-wide essentials** (accessibility, updates)
2. **Admin content management** (asset library, import/export, version control)
3. **Client engagement** (personal dashboard, gamification)
4. **Template registry** (new template types)
5. **Admin collaboration** (screen share, breakout rooms, whiteboard)
6. **Analytics enhancements** (heatmap, reports, leaderboard)
7. **Advanced features** (learning paths, adaptive difficulty, mentors)

